high_descs: Walk through the living room past the couch, make a left around the couch, go into the hallway and door on the left over to the side of the bed near the bed.
Pick up the remotecontrol on the bed.
Walk around the box to the foot of the bed.
Place the remote control into the box that is on the bed.
Pick up the box with the TV remote control from the bed.
Walk out of the bedroom, straight across the hall, into the door to the office, and over near the side of the desk.
Put the box with the TV remote control onto the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the RemoteControl in the Box on the Desk.

high_descs: Turn around and head across the room and turn left to reach the bedroom on the left to reach the bed.
Pick up the remote control from the bed.
Turn right to face the box.
Put the remote control in the box.
Pick up the box from the bed.
Turn right and head to the desk across the passage.
Put the box on the desk.
anns.task_desc: Put the box with the remote control on the desk.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the wall in the opposite side of the hall, passing along a table in the way, then go left to a cross section, go to the left entrance, and get to the side of the bed by a tall lamp.
Pick up the remotecontrol from the bed.
Move to a shorter side of the box.
Place the remotecontrol inside the box on the bed.
Pick up the box from the bed.
Leave the room, continue to the opposite room and step right in front of the desk right after the entrance.
Hide the box under the desk.
anns.task_desc: Hide the RemoteControl inside the Box next to the Desk.
